\end_inset

 shows an example for a timing diagram of different inventory rounds between
 a single RFID reader and different tag reply situations.
 The reader starts with a 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Query
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 command.
 In this command, the reader broadcast the current frame length for all
 the tags in the reading area.
 Each tag has to choose a random slot between 0 and 
\begin_inset Formula $2^{Q}-1$
\end_inset

.
 
